<plot>Glenn Close introduces the audience to the story of South Pacific and its origins as a book, a Broadway musical, a 1958 movie musical, and how and why the 2001 version on ABC came to pass. Interviews with cast &amp; production team, behind-the-scenes footage, Glenn Close's personal behind-the-scenes videos, and clips from the film complete the narrative.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?508433</url></doc>
